11. Content Projection
12. onPush Change Detection
13. Route Guards, Pre-loads, Lazy-loading
14. Custom Pipes
15. @viewChild and @ContentChild Decorators
16. Dynamic Components and ng-template
17. @Host @Hostbinding and exportAs
